msgstr "预期结果：显示两个包的版本信息，确认安装成功。"

msgid ""
"If deploying a multi-node environment, set up the environment on each node."
msgstr "如果部署多节点环境，请在每个节点上配置环境。"

msgid ""
"For more details, please refer to the [Installation "
"Guide](../../installation.md)."
msgstr "更多详情，请参考[安装指南](../../installation.md)。"

msgid "## 5 Online Service Deployment"
msgstr "## 5 在线服务部署"

msgid "### 5.1 Single-Node Online Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.1 单节点在线部署"

msgid ""
"Single-node deployment completes both Prefill and Decode within the same "
"node. The model `Qwen3-Next-80B-A3B-Instruct` can be deployed on 1 Atlas 800"
" A3 (64G × 16)."
msgstr ""
"单节点部署在同一节点内完成 Prefill 和 Decode。模型 `Qwen3-Next-80B-A3B-Instruct` 可部署在 1 个 "
"Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) 上。"

msgid ""
"While a single-node setup supports all input/output scenarios, consider "
"deploying multinodes for optimal performance."
msgstr "虽然单节点设置支持所有输入/输出场景，但为了获得最佳性能，请考虑部署多节点。"

