msgstr "性能结果为："

msgid "## 9 Performance Tuning"
msgstr "## 9 性能调优"

msgid "### 9.1 Recommended Configurations"
msgstr "### 9.1 推荐配置"

msgid ""
"> **Note**:\n"
">\n"
"> - The following configurations are validated in specific test environments and are for reference only. The optimal configuration depends on factors such as maximum input/output length, prefix cache hit rate, precision requirements, and deployment machine ratios. It is recommended to refer to Section 9.2 for tuning based on actual conditions.\n"
">\n"
"> - Qwen3-Next does not support TP>=16 now. Since this model has 16 query heads but only 2 key and value heads, GQA degenerates into MHA when TP >= 16. However, the FIA operator currently fails to function in MHA scenarios with a head dimension of 256 (which is the case for this model)."
msgstr ""
"> **注意**:\n"
">\n"
"> - 以下配置在特定测试环境中验证通过，仅供参考。最佳配置取决于最大输入/输出长度、前缀缓存命中率、精度要求以及部署机器配比等因素。建议根据实际情况参考第9.2节进行调优。\n"
">\n"
"> - Qwen3-Next 当前不支持 TP>=16。由于该模型有16个查询头，但仅有2个键值头，当 TP >= 16 时，GQA 退化为 MHA。然而，FIA 算子目前无法在头维度为256（该模型的情况）的 MHA 场景下正常工作。"

msgid "#### Table 1: Scenario Overview"
msgstr "#### 表1：场景概览"

msgid ""
"|Scenario|Deployment Mode|*Total NPUs|Weight Version|Key Considerations|\n"
"|--------|---------------|-----------|--------------|------------------|\n"
"|High Throughput<br>(16K context)|Single-Node Mixed|2 (A3)|Qwen3-Next|Use tp2 for high-resolution text inputs|\n"
"|Long Context<br>(128K, no prefix cache)|Single-Node Mixed|2 (A3)|Qwen3-Next|tp2 for high-resolution text inputs|\n"
"|Long Context<br>(128K, with prefix cache)|Single-Node Mixed|2 (A3)|Qwen3-Next|tp2 for high-resolution text inputs|\n"
"|Multimodal<br>(1080P)|Single-Node Mixed|2 (A3)|Qwen3-Next|tp2 for high-resolution visual inputs|"
msgstr ""
"|场景|部署模式|*NPU总数|权重版本|关键考量|\n"
"|--------|---------------|-----------|--------------|------------------|\n"
"|高吞吐<br>(16K上下文)|单节点混合|2 (A3)|Qwen3-Next|高分辨率文本输入使用tp2|\n"
"|长上下文<br>(128K，无前缀缓存)|单节点混合|2 (A3)|Qwen3-Next|高分辨率文本输入使用tp2|\n"
"|长上下文<br>(128K，有前缀缓存)|单节点混合|2 (A3)|Qwen3-Next|高分辨率文本输入使用tp2|\n"
"|多模态<br>(1080P)|单节点混合|2 (A3)|Qwen3-Next|高分辨率视觉输入使用tp2|"

msgid ""
"> `*Total NPUs` indicates the total number of NPUs used across all nodes. 1 "
"node = 1 Atlas 800 A3 server (64G × 16 NPUs)."
msgstr "> `*NPU总数` 表示所有节点使用的NPU总数。1个节点 = 1台 Atlas 800 A3 服务器（64G × 16 NPU）。"

msgid "#### Table 2: Detailed Node Configuration"
msgstr "#### 表2：详细节点配置"

msgid ""
"|Scenario|Configuration|NPUs|TP|DP|Max Model Len|MTP Speculation Num|\n"
"|--------|-------------|-----|--|--|-------------------|--------------------|\n"
"|High Throughput / Low Latency (16K)|Server / Single Machine|2|1|1|~16K|3|\n"
"|Long Context (128K, no cache)|Server / Single Machine|2|1|1|128K|3|\n"
"|Long Context (128K, with cache)|Server / Single Machine|2|1|1|128K|3|\n"
"|Multimodal (1080P)|Server / Single Machine|2|1|1|~16K|3|"
msgstr ""
"|场景|配置|NPU数|TP|DP|最大模型长度|MTP推测数量|\n"
"|--------|-------------|-----|--|--|-------------------|--------------------|\n"
"|高吞吐/低延迟 (16K)|服务器/单机|2|1|1|~16K|3|\n"
"|长上下文 (128K，无缓存)|服务器/单机|2|1|1|128K|3|\n"
"|长上下文 (128K，有缓存)|服务器/单机|2|1|1|128K|3|\n"
"|多模态 (1080P)|服务器/单机|2|1|1|~16K|3|"

